  "html": "\n<div><center>\n<table bordercolor=\"#000080\">\n<tr>\n<td><font><img src=\"../images/R.gif\"/> <strong>Tra-la-la...</strong></font><hr noshade=\"\"/>\n<p><font>cf. \"tra la, tra la, la, la, la\n        laire,\" from Theophile Gautier's \"Variations\n        sur le Carnaval de Venise.\"</font></p>\n<p><font><em>reference topics</em></font></p>\n<table>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"../../GautierProject/Carnaval_TG.htm\"><font>\"Carnaval de Venise\"</font></a></td>\n<td><a href=\"../../GautierProject/Carnaval_TG.htm\"><img src=\"../images/arrowry.gif\"/></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"../../GautierProject/Carnaval_TGEN.htm\"><font>\"Carnaval\n                de Venise\"</font></a><font> </font><a href=\"Carnaval_TG%20-%20EN.htm\"><font><img src=\"../images/EN.gif\"/></font></a></td>\n<td><a href=\"../../GautierProject/Carnaval_TG%20-%20EN.htm\"><img src=\"../images/arrowry.gif\"/></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"Carnaval.htm\"><font>\"Carnaval\" and \"Burbank\"</font></a></td>\n<td><a href=\"Carnaval.htm\"><img src=\"../images/arrowry.gif\"/></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Eliot and the quatrain form</td>\n<td><img src=\"../images/arrowry.gif\"/></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"Burbank_A.htm\"><font>back to \"Burbank\" </font></a></td>\n<td><a href=\"Burbank_A.htm\"><img src=\"../images/arrowry.gif\"/></a></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</center></div>\n",
